Mojolicious-Command-generate-bootstrap version 0.01
===================================================

This is just an easy mojo-Command-Extension to easily deploy the Twitter Bootstrap Library
into your Mojolicious-App.

Bundled with this Module is Version 2.3.0 of the Twitter Bootstrap Library.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

USAGE

chdir into your Mojolicious App and run:
   mojo generate bootstrap

This will unwrap following files into your $APPHOME:

   $APPHOME/public/css/bootstrap.min.css
   $APPHOME/public/js/bootstrap.min.js
   $APPHOME/public/img/glyphicons-halflings.png
   $APPHOME/public/img/glyphicons-halflings-white.png

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

	Mojolicious 3.11

